    public interface CompileTimePass
extends Function<DAG<IRVertex,IREdge>,DAG<IRVertex,IREdge>>, Serializable
    Interface for compile-time optimization passes that processes the DAG. It is a function that takes an original DAG to produce a processed DAG, after an optimization.
